invalid type: string "Discuss why do bone and muscle mass differ between individuals, and\n\nhow do they contribute to the overall body weight?\n\n3.4.1 The musculoskeletal system in action\n\nActivity 3.5: Let us observe Move different parts of your body and observe what movement(s) it can make.\n\nTable 3.5: Different types of movements our body can make\n\nBody parts\n\nComplete rotation\n\n in